Package: blockr.audit
Title: An Audit Trail Extension for 'blockr'
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    c(person(given = "David",
             family = "Granjon",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "david@cynkra.com"),
      person(family = "Bristol Myers Squibb",
             role = "fnd")
    )
Description: Building on the docking layout manager provided by 'blockr.dock', this
    provides an extension that records an audit trail of board operations (block
    executions, parameter changes, errors) with timestamps and provenance metadata.
    The trail can be viewed as a log table, exported for compliance reporting, and
    optionally restored across sessions.
